issue.title: chore: Enable requesting numeric enums in "transport=rest" responses for services supporting this (Java, Go, Python, PHP, TypeScript, C#, and Ruby), even if they do not yet turn on REST transport
issue.body:

These are in the process of being removed from Mozilla's trust store. TrustCor's root certificates are being removed pursuant to an investigation prompted by media reporting that TrustCor's ownership also operated a business that produced spyware.
